{"tid":1231413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學生動源呼籲市民繼續留守金鐘","createTime":"2019-06-16T12:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T14:00:13.000Z","uid":73092,"like":70,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ac5fcaa63bd0f475a7c7b22ad079c7c33e6cddf6","tid":1231413,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:48:45.000Z","msg":"【不撤不散】<br />\n學生動源呼籲市民繼續留守金鐘，即使林鄭月娥已向香港市民道歉，但仍未宣布撤回送中法案，亦未撤控所有因反送中示威被控市民的控罪。 <br />\n<br />\n學生動源要求政府以下三點：<br />\n1.撤回送中法案 <br />\n2.撤銷6&middot;12示威定性暴動決定 <br />\n3.撤銷所有因反送中示威被控的市民所有控罪<br />\n<br />\n學生動源<br />\n2019年6月16日"},{"pid":"80ee04643274da6ddf239b7bcc7f9a75ca350ad6","tid":1231413,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:49:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4c7b731e3efa77b5243234733f0992554b9f60","tid":1231413,"uid":46885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:50:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"97eb2252bbe1fbf081e8c22da0e66abccfe32a38","tid":1231413,"uid":44698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:52:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1c5d6b54437e79acf8d70335ab7704e0378039c5","tid":1231413,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:52:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7231cc3e195d3d013b6782af6659e2d08a2c00f0","tid":1231413,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad20ab6f148f49d79693933ed5fe5fe99afcec1a","tid":1231413,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:11:01.000Z","msg":"行上去禮賓府啦<br />\n得返20個黑警唔夠<br />\n你哋留喺下面條馬路等乜?"},{"pid":"61302478c785e038ee79014364f4703d5dccede9","tid":1231413,"uid":3860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:11:28.000Z","msg":"一定要佢撤消檢控69 612 示威者 同追究黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm